data.description: Nice 4 bedroom home in a great neighborhood. Property sits in a Cul-de-sac and is walking distance to Ashton Ranch School. Modern kitchen with stainless appliances, soft water system, fans in all bedrooms, paid for Solar and the Ac unit was replaced in May 2022. Small touches include Crown moldings, upgraded baseboards, vinyl plank flooring and artificial turf in the backyard.
